    "Image Track File that contains 1 minute of 4K flat frames. Each frame consists of 3 sets of three patches, with the sets stacked vertically and the patches arranged horizontally.": "包含1分钟4K Flat帧的图像轨迹文件。每一帧包含3组，每组3个色块，垂直堆叠，水平排列。",
